OC(=O)c1ccc2ccccc2c1O                                    Xinafoate (1-hydroxy-2-naphthoate)
OC(=O)c1c(O)c2ccccc2cc1Cc1cc2ccccc2c(O)c1C(=O)O          Pamoate / embonate
OCC(O)C1OC(=O)C(O)=C1O                                   Ascorbate
OC(=O)c1cc(=O)[nH]c(=O)[nH]1                                  Orotate
OC(=O)C(N)CCC(=O)O                                       Glutamate
OC(=O)C(N)CC(=O)O                                        Aspartate

