NCCO                                                     Ethanolamine
OCCNCCO                                                  Diethanolamine
OCCN(CCO)CCO                                             Triethanolamine
CN(C)CCO                                                 Deanol (dimethylaminoethanol)
[N](C)(C)(C)CCO                                          Choline
[N](C)(C)(C)CC(=O)O                                      Betaine
NCCN                                                     Ethylenediamine
C1CNCCN1                                                 Piperazine
C1COCCN1                                                 Morpholine
CN1CCOCC1                                                N-Methylmorpholine
C1CCCCC1NC1CCCCC1                                        Dicyclohexylamine
CNCC(O)C(O)C(O)C(O)CO                                    Meglumine (N-methylglucamine)
OCC(N)(CO)CO                                             Tromethamine (TRIS)
c1ccccc1CNCCc1ccccc1                                     Benethamine
